  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nTransaction decoder (TxDecoder class) contains too many logic, it handles all the tx types, signing, and new network form does not add to clarity. There is a change transactions can be optimized in terms of allocations also.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nTxDecoder class should be decoupled, approaches to consider:\r\n- separate type and form detection from transaction fields decoding\r\n- separate network wrapper decoding\r\n- separate signature related code\r\n- have a decoding type per transaction\r\n- transactions become structs\r\n- make it partial\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nCode generation - seems hard to do due to numerous special cases faced during decoding/encoding\r\n",
